{"tid":2488942,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"財經新聞：臥龍基金「連燈力」於開市後以$100.66再次撈底Unity！潛伏一天再次出擊！高於４成勝率！","createTime":"2021-04-14T14:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T18:40:14.000Z","uid":149018,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"02e42f746afd3489c3f7f949636cd4c16a287857","tid":2488942,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"第三十二次軍議<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPJ2Saef1gW8zJBj2JfAwB6by6qXQ3uEc375mKKTaGdjD?filename=PBUYGnc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPBUYGnc.jpg&h=beec74af&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaGVMLUjFEF8L6jFZtyTi94ioW8C5LyC2y9WPHN5HSzBQ?filename=mqyuN2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqyuN2c.jpg&h=e1bdd360&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呂布第三十一戰與進攻MSFT以微小盈利以$257.31獲勝後第三十二戰軍議因缺少天時地利人和延遲操作，於隔天開市後以$100.66再次以精明眼光進攻Unity。<br />\n<br />\n至於眾將為之興奮之Coinbase則考慮以二軍隱密攻之，歡迎交流。<br />\n<br />\n呂布軍「連燈力」目前戰況31戰13勝18敗，勝率現為41.94%！<br />\n目前「連燈力」呂布狀態：<br />\n目前「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"green\">688.69</span>HP 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">-31.13</span>%<br />\n<br />\n呂布潛伏一秋後復出，智力不變，武力100 智力67操盤，請絕對相信本將軍判斷。<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"green\">呂布曰：軍師團人去樓空火熱不再，奉先該研究營軍之策。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdFimGqBxfLuoByRR1NhVeiZmxN4geWTCGCJ28oUNfuhG?filename=pRzBs5r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpRzBs5r.jpg&h=01f361f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27016bb9a6d3f133c377e56b3ed462effda952d9","tid":2488942,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02e42f746afd3489c3f7f949636cd4c16a287857","tid":2488942,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"第三十二次軍議<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PBUYGnc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPBUYGnc.jpg&h=beec74af&s={SIZE}\" /